fields.name: Mikalla Cleansing And Conditioning Shampoo
fields.description: Mikalla Cleansing and Conditioning Shampoo gently cleanses all dirt and residue from hair without stripping off essential nutrients. It contains a highly versatile formula with a blend of quality conditioning agents that will leave your hair healthier, shinier and silky. This gentle yet effective shampoo has an exemplary spread and lathering features that leave your hair feeling soft and full of body. It is also enhanced with vitamin B5 that improves the strength of your hair, whilst nurturing and restoring natural moisture.

fields.name: Miadi Fruity Shampoo
fields.description: MIADI Fruity Shampoo is a 2-in-1 product that cleanses and conditions hair to leave it soft and manageable. It is formulated to gently wash away impurities without stripping natural oils, making hair stronger and less prone to breakage. It has a pleasant scent, and is specifically designed to nourish and moisturize different needs of African hair.

fields.name: Zoe Shampoo Anti Dandruff
fields.description: Zoe Anti‑Dandruff Shampoo gently soothes an itchy scalp and reduces flakes, leaving hair clean and refreshed thanks to piroctone olamine that targets Malassezia, ichthyol pale for anti‑inflammatory action, tea tree oil to calm irritation, wheat protein for strength and shine, and panthenol to hydrate, all in a sulfate‑free base safe for color‑treated hair.

fields.name: Tre Semmé Luxurious Shampoo
fields.description: Tressemé Luxurious Shampoo delivers a spa‑like experience that leaves hair feeling irresistibly silty, thanks to a blend of nourishing ingredients: argan oil supplies deep moisture and shine, hydrolyzed keratin rebuilds weakened strands, panthenol (vitamin B5) boosts hydration and elasticity, and a hint of rosemary extract stimulates the scalp for healthier growth, all wrapped in a sulfate‑free, pH‑balanced formula that respects color‑treated hair while imparting a delicate, lingering fragrance.

fields.name: Cosmo Avocado Shampoo
fields.description: Cosmo Avocado Shampoo is infused with the goodness of avocado, deeply nourishing and hydrating your hair, leaving it soft and revitalized. Perfect for dry and damaged hair, this shampoo provides the necessary moisture to restore your hair's health. With its gentle formula, it's suitable for daily use.

fields.name: Mikalla Honey & Butter Conditioner
fields.description: Mikalla Honey & Butter Hair Conditioner Detangler is a light and non-greasy cream that soothes dry itchy scalp. Contains anti-bacterial and anti-fungal properties which keep your scalp free from dandruff. Also rich in natural ingredients that improve the texture of your hair. Ideal for protecting your hair against the effects of heat treatment. Enriched with natural herbs that repair split ends, revive damaged hair and promote hair growth.

fields.name: Sheba Instant conditioner
fields.description: Suitable for all hair types and ages, including natural, relaxed, and color-treated hair. It works to separate tangles, cut detangling time in half, and can be used as a co-wash for frequent cleansing. To effectively use the conditioner, apply it on your hair and leave it in for 10 minutes, use your fingers to detangle or the wide tooth comb.

fields.name: ORS Oil Repleneshing Conditioner
fields.description: The ORS Replenishing Conditioner deeply penetrates to restore moisture and add shine to the hair scalp. Formulated with Olive Oil, Sweet Orange Oil and Marine Proteins, this conditioner fortifies and balances moisture and protein levels, resulting in stronger, healthier hair that is shiny and manageable. Suitable for all hair types.

fields.name: Tre Semmé Anti Breakage Conditioner
fields.description: Tresemmé Anti‑Breakage Conditioner is formulated to fortify fragile strands and reduce snapping, leaving hair noticeably stronger, smoother and more resilient. Enriched with hydrolyzed keratin, argan oil and a blend of conditioning agents, it penetrates the cortex to rebuild weakened fibers while coating each hair shaft with a lightweight, non‑greasy film that detangles and protects against everyday stressors.

fields.name: Creme of Nature Cleansing Conditioner
fields.description: This moisturizing formula is an intensive deep conditioning treatment that strengthens and helps prevent breakage, while detangling and adding shine. Ideal for all hair types, this treatment can be used after every shampoo as a quick conditioner or every week as a re-constructor for noticeably healthy hair that you can see and feel.

fields.name: Mikalla Hair Mayonnaise
fields.description: Mikalla Mayonnaise is a deep conditioning hair treatment designed to nourish and revive dry, damaged hair using ingredients like olive oil, shea butter, and vitamins. It provides intense moisture, helps detangle and control frizz, and protects hair from heat damage, ultimately leaving it softer, smoother, and more manageable.

fields.name: Mikalla Leave In Treatment
fields.description: The Mikalla Total Moisture Boost Leave-In Treatment is specially formulated to invigorate, moisturize, detangle and protect hair. It is enriched with menthol (helps soothe itchy scalps), shea butter (works as a great sealant & heat protectant) and castor oil (moisturizes and thickens hair while reducing breakage).

fields.name: Mega Growth Deep Treatment
fields.description: This deep conditioner infuses natural oils (olive, shea, avocado, coconut, argan) and conditioning proteins into each strand to defend against breakage, split ends and dryness. Its ultra‑protective blend strengthens hair from within, restores softness and shine, and adds anti‑breakage agents that shield against styling stress. For best results, apply generously to damp, shampoo‑cleaned hair from roots to ends, leave on 10 minutes (or longer with heat for deeper penetration), then rinse.

fields.name: Tony Airo Siri Leave In Treatment
fields.description: Siri Natural Hair Moisturizing Leave‑In Treatment delivers deep, plant‑based hydration with amla, aloe vera, curry leaf, hibiscus and rose oils to lock in moisture, soothe the scalp, fight dandruff and support healthy growth—repairing damage and taming frizz for all hair types, including natural, dreadlocks and mixed‑race hair, with optional henna for extra shine.

fields.name: Miadi Leave In Treatment
fields.description: This lightweight, non‑greasy leave‑in detangles and smooths, making combing easier and reducing breakage while sealing in moisture to prevent frizz and split ends. It fortifies strands against styling and environmental stress, softens hair, and maintains hydration without heavy buildup. Versatile enough for use as a styling primer, alongside other treatments, or on its own, the formula is specifically tailored to meet the needs of textured African hair.

fields.name: Black Essentials Leave In Treatment
fields.description: A lightweight, nourishing formula designed to hydrate, strengthen, and protect your hair, available with Argan Oil or Olive Oil. It deeply moisturizes and revitalizes dry, damaged, frizzy, and brittle hair while enhancing its natural shine and softness, reducing breakage and split ends.

fields.name: TCB Deep Penetrating Treatment
fields.description: TCB Naturals Deep Penetrating Treatment blends shea butter and honey to revitalize dry, damaged, and chemically treated hair, penetrating the shaft to condition and moisturize for stronger, healthier strands. After shampooing and towel‑drying, apply the treatment generously throughout the hair, leave on for 10–15 minutes (or longer with a heat cap for extremely damaged hair), then rinse with warm water and style as desired.

fields.name: ORS Olive Oil Hold and Shine Wrap Mousse
fields.description: ORS Olive Oil Wrap/Set Hair Mousse is a lightweight, fluffy foam that moisturizes and adds shine to hair while providing hold. With olive oil rich in Vitamin E and panthenol, it smooths wrapping and molding, extends roller sets, and speeds up drying time for a flawless finish. The convenient pump dispenses a airy texture that penetrates quickly, leaving hair supple, manageable, and ready for styling.

fields.name: Mikalla Styling gel
fields.description: Mikalla Styling Gel is an elegant smooth gel that gives your hair an ultra-strong styling hold. It has a strong resistance to humidity whilst leaving your hair with a non-tacky, flake-free lustrous shine. It is lcohol-free, paraben-free, and hypoallergenic, making it perfect for everyday styling, slick backs, ponytails, and edge control on sensitive scalps.

fields.name: Nice & Lovely Firm Hold
fields.description: This extra‑firm hold styling gel gives you maximum, long‑lasting control for any look, while an alcohol‑free, non‑sticky, non‑flaking formula keeps hair comfortable and flake‑free. Enriched with vitamins and a blend of olive and amla oils, it conditions and strengthens, delivering a smooth, glossy shine that reduces breakage, tames frizz and prevents fly aways.

fields.name: Movit Curl Activator Gel
fields.description: Movit Curl Activator is a hair gel designed to define, enhance, and moisturize natural curls without causing stiffness or flaking. Its formula, enriched with glycerin, provides a soft-to-medium hold that makes hair manageable, shiny, and frizz-free, ideal for styles like wash-and-go and twist-outs.

fields.name: Alisons Coconut and Olive Hair Food
fields.description: Alison’s Coconut & Olive Oil Hair Food with Sunscreen is a lightweight, nutrient‑rich treatment that blends pure coconut oil and extra‑virgin olive oil with UV protection. It delivers deep moisture, seals in shine, fortifies strands against breakage, and guards hair from sun‑induced fading and dryness. Enriched with vitamin E and natural antioxidants, it smooths frizz, reduces fly aways, and leaves hair soft, supple, and resilient—ideal for all hair types as a daily leave‑in or weekly intensive mask.

fields.name: TCB Naturals Nourishing Hair Food
fields.description: TCB Naturals Nourishing Hair Food is a rich blend of natural ingredients, including olive oil, shea butter, and vitamins, that deeply nourishes and moisturizes hair. It helps repair dryness, reduces breakage, and adds shine, leaving hair soft, manageable, and healthy-looking. Suitable for all hair types, it can be used as a leave-in treatment or styling aid to detangle, smooth, and protect hair from environmental stressors.

fields.name: Miadi Hair Food
fields.description: Miadi hair food is a nourishing hair product enriched with Vitamin E and beeswax to moisturize, strengthen, and protect hair, suitable for all hair types. It helps to balance scalp oils, prevent excessive flaking, and reduce breakage, leading to more manageable, soft, and shiny hair. It can also be used by men to keep their hair looking fresh and flake-free.

fields.name: Mega Growth Profectiv Anti-Breakage Hair Growth oil
fields.description: Profectiv Mega Growth Oil is an anti-breakage hair oil designed to strengthen hair and promote healthier growth. It is formulated with natural oils and conditioning proteins to reduce breakage, nourish the scalp, and protect against damage from heat styling and chemical treatments. This oil can be used as a hot oil treatment or a daily moisturizer to help improve hair's softness, manageability, and shine.

fields.name: Dabur Amla Hair Oil
fields.description: Dabur Amla Hair Oil is a traditional hair oil infused with the goodness of Indian Gooseberry (Amla), which strengthens hair from root to tip, promotes healthy growth, and adds shine. It is a blend of natural extracts and oils designed to nourish and strengthen hair, reduce hair fall, and improve texture, with the original version also containing other natural ingredients and a secret traditional formula.

fields.name: Stylin Dredz Mouldin' Gel Wax
fields.description: Stylin' Dredz Mouldin' Gel Wax is a maximum hold styling product designed for creating and maintaining dreadlocks. It locks hair into place to create neat, durable locs without flaking. The formula is enriched with tea tree oil and glycerine to moisturize and condition the scalp, helping to eliminate dryness and prevent buildup.

fields.name: Simple Kind to Kind Moisturising Cleanser
fields.description: The Simple Kind to Skin Hydrating Light Moisturiser is a lightweight, fast-absorbing cream that provides up to 12 hours of hydration and is formulated for all skin types, especially sensitive skin. It contains Pro-Vitamin B5 and Vitamin E and is free from artificial colors, perfumes, and harsh chemicals.

fields.name: Nivea Perfect and Radiant 3 in 1 cleanser
fields.description: The NIVEA Perfect & Radiant 3-in-1 Cleanser 150ml is a multi-purpose product designed to cleanse, exfoliate, and brighten the skin. It is formulated with magnolia extract and natural white clay to gently remove impurities, makeup, and dead skin cells while helping to control shine and mattify the skin

fields.name: Mizizi Rose Water
fields.description: Mizizi Rose Water is a natural, alcohol‑free toner free of artificial fragrances and harsh chemicals. It hydrates and refreshes the skin, helps control oil, and leaves a subtle floral scent. The versatile formula can be used on hair—mixed with aloe vera for frizz or combined with oils like grapeseed and vegetable glycerin for a spritz. Apply after cleansing as a toner, or blend with bentonite clay for a soothing face mask.

fields.name: L'Oréal Paris fine flowers toner
fields.description: The L'Oréal Paris Fine Flowers Toner is a gentle, alcohol-free toner for normal to dry sensitive skin that cleanses and refreshes with rose and jasmine flower extracts. It removes the last traces of impurities, soothes the skin, and helps it feel soft and comfortable. This ensures a soft, comfortable and fresh skin, every day

fields.name: Garnier Micellar Cleansing water
fields.description: Garnier micellar cleansing water is an all-in-1 cleanser and makeup remover that uses micelle technology to lift dirt and impurities without harsh rubbing or rinsing. Contains micelles that act like magnets, trapping and lifting away dirt, oil, and makeup without the need for harsh rubbing or rinsing.

fields.name: Uncover Licorice Dark Spot serum
fields.description: The Uncover Licorice Root Dark Spot Serum is a targeted skincare product designed to improve hyperpigmentation and even skin tone by fading dark spots and post-blemish marks. It uses a potent formula with key ingredients like 2% arbutin, 2% tranexamic acid, 1% kojic acid, and 2% niacinamide, which work to inhibit melanin production, brighten the skin, and reduce the appearance of discoloration.

fields.name: Nivea Q10 Serum
fields.description: Nivea Q10 serum is a concentrated treatment delivers a quick boost of skin‑cell energy and reinforces the skin’s inner structure, visibly smoothing fine lines and wrinkles—sometimes in as little as five minutes. Formulated with pure Coenzyme Q10 and Bioxifill® peptides to stimulate collagen, it works well as a makeup base or a pre‑cream step in any anti‑aging routine.

fields.name: Garnier Vitamin C Booster Serum
fields.description: Garnier Vitamin C Booster Serum is a concentrated facial serum designed to brighten the skin and reduce dark spots. It features a potent blend of 3.5% Vitamin C, Niacinamide, and Salicylic Acid to create a more even skin tone and enhance the skin's natural glow. This lightweight, fast-absorbing formula is intended to help with hyperpigmentation, provide antioxidant protection, and is suitable for daily use, day and night.

fields.name: L'Oreal Paris Revitalift hydrating Serum
fields.description: The Revitalift Filler serum uses a high concentration of Hyaluronic Acid to intensely hydrate, plump, and smooth the skin, with macro and micro molecules working at different levels. It features a firming complex and Adenosine to reduce wrinkles and firm the skin. Both serums are designed to be lightweight, non-greasy, absorb quickly, and can be used morning and night before moisturizer.

fields.name: Luron Acne Control Pimple Cream
fields.description: This is a lightweight, fast-absorbing spot treatment that uses active ingredients like Salicylic Acid, Vitamin B3, and Neem to fight acne. It is designed to reduce inflammation, soothe irritation, and fade post-acne marks, helping to achieve clearer, more even-toned skin.

fields.name: Nivea Soft Moisturing Cream
fields.description: Nivea Soft Moisturising Cream is a light, dermatologically approved, pH-neutral cream. It has a fast-absorbing formula enriched with Vitamin E and jojoba oil, making skin feel soft, smooth, and hydrated. It is suitable for all skin types and can be used on the face, body, and hands.

fields.name: Simple Hydrating moisturizer
fields.description: The Simple Hydrating Light Moisturizer is a lightweight, fast-absorbing moisturizer designed for sensitive skin that provides up to 12 hours of hydration and leaves skin feeling soft and smooth. It is formulated with skin-loving ingredients like pro-vitamin B5 and vitamin E, and contains no artificial colors, perfumes, or harsh chemicals.

fields.name: Uncover Argan Hydrating Moisturiser
fields.description: Contains a lightweight, hydrating formula with active ingredients like 3% Squalane, 2% Niacinamide, 1% African Argan Oil, Hyaluronic Acid, and Moringa Extract. It is designed to deeply moisturize, nourish, and protect the skin barrier while brightening dullness, minimizing breakouts, and improving skin texture without clogging pores. The moisturizer is suitable for all skin types and should be applied generously twice daily after cleansing.

fields.name: Nivea Perfect and Radiant Night Cream
fields.description: NIVEA Perfect & Radiant Night Cream is designed to restore skin's natural tone and radiance overnight by increasing cell renewal and regenerating the skin. Key benefits include a softer, smoother feel, enhanced radiance, and visibly reduced dark marks. Its formula, which includes Eventone Pure Active and Pro Vitamin B5, works to restore a more even tone and provides lasting moisture.

fields.name: Luron Replenishing Night Cream
fields.description: Luron replenishing night cream is a rich, restorative night cream designed to deeply hydrate, nourish, and revitalize the skin while you sleep. It works to combat signs of aging by reducing fine lines and wrinkles, improving firmness, and evening out skin tone. Key ingredients often include vitamins A, E, and B3, as well as lemon and botanical extracts, and it's formulated to be non-greasy and absorb quickly.

fields.name: Garnier Skin Active Green Tea Facing Sheet Mask
fields.description: Garnier Skin Active Green Tea Hydrating face sheet mask this mask hydrates, soothes, and rebalances combination skin by providing intense moisture with hyaluronic acid and green tea extract. Its key benefits include reducing shine, purifying the skin, and leaving it feeling refreshed and looking more radiant. The mask helps to diminish the appearance of fine lines and pores, while also maintaining a healthy moisture balance for a clear and luminous complexion.

fields.name: Face Facts Smoothing Honey Peel Off mask
fields.description: The Face Facts Smoothing Honey Peel Off Mask is a vegan-friendly, 60ml mask that uses honey extract and glycerin to cleanse, moisturize, and brighten the skin. It is designed to soften the skin, lock in moisture, and leave it feeling hydrated and revitalized. To use, apply a thin, even layer to clean skin, avoid the eye and lip areas, leave it on for about 20 minutes until dry, and then carefully peel it off.

fields.name: Beauty Clinic Aloevera Mud Mask
fields.description: This is a deep-cleansing, detoxifying treatment enriched with clay, gold mica, and aloe vera. It is designed to exfoliate the skin, remove blackheads and impurities, and tighten the skin to reveal a clearer, more radiant complexion. The mask also provides a soothing effect, a detoxifying action from its mineral- and vitamin-rich ingredients, and helps tackle the signs of skin aging.

fields.name: Uncover I am Beau-Tea-Ful Green Tea Detoxifying sheet mask
fields.description: A 20-minute treatment designed to detoxify and clarify skin using the antioxidant properties of green tea. It helps minimize the appearance of pores, combat the effects of pollution, and provides an instant glow and hydration. The mask is suitable for all skin types and is used after cleansing and toning, with results including refreshed and radiant skin.

fields.name: Himalayan Detox Charcoal Mask
fields.description: A skincare product designed to deep cleanse, purify, and detoxify the skin. It typically features activated charcoal to draw out impurities, dirt, and excess oil from pores, with common additions like green tea or natural clays to further refine the skin and prevent clogging. These masks are ideal for oily or combination skin types, helping to reduce blackheads, blemishes, and shine, and are often used once or twice a week for a refreshed, smoother, and clearer complexion.

fields.name: Nivea Sunshine Control spf 50
fields.description: A lightweight, non-greasy facial sunscreen that provides high UV protection while mattifying oily skin. It is designed for daily use on normal/combination skin, offering broad-spectrum UVA/UVB protection against sunburn and premature aging, along with an 8-hour shine-free finish. The formula is ophthalmologically approved, dermatologically approved, and contains a natural antioxidant to protect skin from within.

fields.name: La Roche Posay Anthelios UV Immune Tinted
fields.description: A tinted, ultra-light fluid sunscreen that offers broad-spectrum SPF 50+ protection against UVB, UVA, and ultra-long UVA rays. It is designed for sensitive skin, features an anti-eye-stinging formula, and provides a natural, even finish with a tint that blends into all skin tones without a white cast. The water, sweat, and sand-resistant formula is non-greasy, non-comedogenic, and can be used alone or as a makeup base.

fields.name: Cerave Facial Moisturising lotion (SPF 50)
fields.description: A lightweight, daily moisturizer that provides broad-spectrum UVA/UVB protection, up to 24 hours of hydration, and helps restore the skin's natural barrier. It is formulated with three essential ceramides, hyaluronic acid, and niacinamide, and features CeraVe's MVE technology for a continuous release of moisture. The formula is fragrance-free, paraben-free, non-comedogenic, and suitable for normal to dry or acne-prone skin.

fields.name: Uncover Aloe Invisible Sunscren (SPF 50)
fields.description: A lightweight, broad-spectrum sunscreen that provides high protection against UVA and UVB rays. It is designed for daily use, leaves no white cast, and is formulated with African Aloe Vera and Hyaluronic Acid to hydrate, moisturize, and cool the skin. It helps prevent sun damage, premature aging, and dark spots.

fields.name: Garnier Skin Active Green Tea
fields.description: The Garnier Skin Active SPF 50+ Invisible Serum Sunscreen is designed for daily facial sun protection, offering very high SPF 50+ protection against UVB, UVA, and long UVA rays. Its formulation aims to provide an invisible, lightweight texture that absorbs quickly into the skin, leaving no white cast or greasy residue.

fields.name: Nivea Blueberry Lip Balm
fields.description: A tinted lip balm that provides long-lasting moisture, a subtle shine, and a fruity blackberry flavor. It contains natural oils, like shea butter, and vitamins to keep lips smooth and hydrated for up to 24 hours. The balm is designed to moisturize, repair, and provide a hint of color to enhance the lips' natural beauty.

fields.name: Nivea Classic Lip Balm
fields.description: A caring lip product that provides long-lasting moisture, softness, and protection against dryness. Its formula, enriched with ingredients like shea butter and natural oils, melts into the lips to provide instant hydration and a smooth, supple feel. The balm is designed to be applied throughout the day to maintain moisturization and prevent dryness from environmental factors like cold or wind.

fields.name: Nivea Strawberry  Lip Balm
fields.description: A tinted lip care product that moisturizes lips for up to 24 hours while providing a strawberry aroma, a reddish shine, and a hint of color. Its formula is enriched with natural oils and ingredients like shea butter, which glides on smoothly to leave lips feeling soft, smooth, and kissably soft. It is also available in other formulations that include vitamins C and E for added protection.

fields.name: Anashe LipGloss 601
fields.description: An ultra-shiny, transparent color gloss that gives lips a radiant and sparkling fresh look with just one coat. It is described as ultra-portable and easy to use, designed to provide a high-shine, luxurious finish. It can be worn alone for a fresh sparkle or layered over lipstick.

fields.name: Zaron New Luxurious Lip gloss Sugarplum
fields.description: A high-performance, long-lasting lip gloss that delivers rich color and a healthy, glossy shine. It is described as a sheer, nude-colored gloss with a buildable, pigment-rich formula. It is designed to give the lips a “crystal pout” and an extra “juicy, luminous” look. The product comes with a doe-foot applicator for comfortable and easy wear.
